    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164330/extras/765aca259a33383c186e27842a99074c.avif?t=1769762338\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164330/extras_big/765aca259a33383c186e27842a99074c.avif?t=1769762338 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164330/extras/c42fbfe6cf0aefb8684fd0c0e10120bd.avif?t=1769762338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164330/extras/1be6fd616abdfa90d12b48abcc9bb506.avif?t=1769762338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164330/extras/cc747828000796671235e816c7f305d4.avif?t=1769762338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164330/extras/929025c2b7d8683d2b3d9bf52b689ae3.avif?t=1769762338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164330/extras/436edb48667cca22c7c451429a40a3b8.avif?t=1769762338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164330/extras/c0ff8e26bbd533c32940f2ad0aa22a82.avif?t=1769762338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《无限暖暖》是由叠纸游戏开发的暖暖系列第五代作品，是一款由UE5引擎打造的多平台开放世界游戏。这是一场收集美好的冒险之旅。暖暖将与大喵一起，利用奇想力与能力套装，与美好的世界牵手，与所有惊喜不期而遇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【主线新篇】祷声起诸大地</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新地区“伊赞之土”现已开放探险。穿过参天巨树造访蜗牛城，在巨人的遗迹开启尘封的故事，龙骨之上，命运被重新书写。欢迎来到新世界，这里每天都有奇迹发生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【开放世界】以奇想探索，每一处风物与传说</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对未知的谜题与挑战，举起弓箭、邀伙伴协战、感悟新的能力套装……都是解法其一。若想描画这个无限世界的边际，请带上灵感、勇气，与好奇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【家园建造】空中有座暖暖的岛</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在专属岛屿，亲手打造理想家园。自由设计每一处空间，种植、采星、养鱼……这里不只是一座岛，更是以奇想力编织的，会呼吸的梦想。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【平台跳跃】每一次跃起，都是新的冒险</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论身处森罗万象的奇迹大陆，还是神秘奇诡的空间幻境，用不同的能力组合解构关卡的精妙设计，在起落之间发现新的奥秘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【休闲玩法】发呆、小憩，做什么都可以</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >钓鱼骑行，撸猫扑蝶，和路人一起躲雨，又或者开一局小游戏......在这里，感受微风与鸟鸣，尽情享受无忧无虑的静谧时光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【联机开放】旅途有回声，灵魂不再独行</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与平行世界的暖暖相遇，共赴一场美好约定。摇铃轻响时，好友便相会。无论是牵手同行，还是自在独往，旅途都充满乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【换装染色】是世界的摄影家，也是调色师</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搭配心仪的色彩和造型，捕捉与世界的共鸣。打开大喵相机，自定义专属滤镜和拍照风格，用照片定格每一个跨越时间的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集美好的开放世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感谢各位对《无限暖暖》的关注，期待与各位在奇迹大陆相遇！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 印度尼西亚语, 日语<strong>*</strong>, 泰语, 简体中文<strong>*</strong>, 繁体中文, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 韩语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
